casebody.data:
Tuesday, August 12, 1997

MOTION DOCKET

97-1618. Ameritech Ohio v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 97-654-TP-CSS. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the appellant’s motion for stay of execution and enforcement of the opinion and order entered by the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio on July 17,1997, and its entry on rehearing entered on July 31,1997,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, denied.

F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., dissent.
